    <dlgPart>
      <portrait>Esbenus</portrait>
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>"Nah. I did twelve years and when you do something for that long, well, it's the only life you know. I was wounded and left for dead. Raiders found me and took me in. No, not out of kindness. They need men badly, especially men with proper fighting experience. While I was recovering, I lived like a lord – food, wine, women, and a soft bed. Then they let me choose and I chose to stay.

"The way I see it, you do the same shit, but the perks are much better."</npc_text>
      <onLoadScripts />
      <answers>
        <dlgAnsw>
          <text>"So, how did you end up here?"</text>
